Class LaGetter

java.lang.Object
  com.ozdevworx.util.LaGetter
Direct Known Subclasses:
ListArray
public class LaGetter
extends java.lang.Object

This class is the getter portion of a com.jdbwc.iface.DataHandler implementation. The getter logic was seperated from the DataHandlers operation logic to reduce class sizes and make the logic easier to work with.

Version:
1.0.0.1
Author:
